{"tid":1809595,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「和你Safe」 整左個去中心化App，希望岩大家用","createTime":"2020-01-03T08:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T10:22:44.000Z","uid":300410,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"4435e301896e62f3953e0ff8e3691a330851d52d","tid":1809595,"uid":300410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T08:22:03.000Z","msg":"Android:  <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.hkers\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.hkers&d=GDp31xM3xvXFOTrKf8Ol7Bq8xf71D2STVxQEH8iwqLk%3D&h=0ec62930\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.hkers</a><br />\nIOS：<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/hkers-messenger/id1484935497?l=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Fhkers-messenger%2Fid1484935497%3Fl%3Den&d=GDp31xM3xvXFOTrKf8Ol7Bq8xf71D2STVxQEH8iwqLk%3D&h=c211fba5\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/hkers-messenger/id1484935497?l=en</a><br />\n<br />\n個App主要係實現：<br />\n-  <strong><ins>去中心化(Decentralized)[</ins>/b]，<br />\n- 即係對話內容[b]<ins>唔會有Server儲存</ins></strong>，<br />\n- 唔用App時內容亦<strong><ins>唔會儲存係手機</ins></strong>入面，只儲存係私人已加密的區域鏈儲存庫，<br />\n- <strong><ins>無需電話號碼登記</ins></strong>，只需用電郵登記一個去中心化既個人賬號，<br />\n- 只透過QR code 或者send link 邀請朋友。<br />\n- 電郵登記方面，我哋使用Blockstack區域鏈系統，具有<strong><ins>身份數據加密及私有</ins></strong>，<strong><ins>100%真正數據所有權</ins></strong>等特征，有興趣的朋友可以睇睇詳細介紹，<a href=\"https://blockstack.org/try-blockstack\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblockstack.org%2Ftry-blockstack&d=GDp31xM3xvXFOTrKf8Ol7Bq8xf71D2STVxQEH8iwqLk%3D&h=f7c6ac07\" target=\"_blank\">https://blockstack.org/try-blockstack</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「和你Safe」功能</span></span>，比如話，你要去行山，可以預先設定一個危險信息&amp;信息發送的對象（可同時發送給多人）&amp;發送時間，如果係設定的時間你未有取消危險信息，HKers會開啟一個一次性既account，將預設既信息發比你指定既朋友，希望最大程度保護到大家的安全。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">對話&amp;其他設置</span></span>方面大家亦可以試試，內容都係去中心化同埋加密既，當然現時只係好base既對話功能，個App而家亦仲有好多地方需要改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，希望大家可以支持下我哋，有D咩問題或者建議歡迎各位比意見去改善。<br />\n<br />\n裝左App可以用哩條Link add我哋，有咩使用上的問題，或者功能上有咩意見，都可以同我哋傾下，<a href=\"https://hkers.page.link/vS6CHnHRh6ndYHB46\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkers.page.link%2FvS6CHnHRh6ndYHB46&d=GDp31xM3xvXFOTrKf8Ol7Bq8xf71D2STVxQEH8iwqLk%3D&h=57031ee0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkers.page.link/vS6CHnHRh6ndYHB46</a><br />\n<br />\n如果大家認同我哋既諗法，亦都可以支持下我哋，<a href=\"https://paypal.me/hkers?locale.x=zh_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpaypal.me%2Fhkers%3Flocale.x%3Dzh_HK&d=GDp31xM3xvXFOTrKf8Ol7Bq8xf71D2STVxQEH8iwqLk%3D&h=36bf4b10\" target=\"_blank\">https://paypal.me/hkers?locale.x=zh_HK</a><br />\n<br />\n下面係簡單screenshot &amp; 介紹：<br />\n<img src=\"http://bit.ly/2MTn4jo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MTn4jo&h=d0e7c982&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://bit.ly/2MPSjeS\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MPSjeS&h=9330baa5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://bit.ly/39E3qSj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F39E3qSj&h=a40338bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cbaf624f408883c07b57ea57d4bde16234557aef","tid":1809595,"uid":42149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T08:23:48.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n多個app"},{"pid":"1804d3af72880c4e734af8a095d5572cd597db13","tid":1809595,"uid":323510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T08:31:48.000Z","msg":"正😍"},{"pid":"d7d01dbccf36de97260021124b64295a0ed917a8","tid":1809595,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T08:45:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.